ethers:
1. Get the total supply of eDOGE tokens

```javascript
const eDOGEContract = await ethers.getContractAt('edoge', 'EDOGE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS');
const totalSupply = await eDOGEContract.totalSupply();
console.log(`Total supply of eDOGE tokens:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(totalSupply, 5));
```

2. Get the balance of a user's eDOGE tokens

```javascript
const userAddress = 'USER_ADDRESS';
const userBalance = await eDOGEContract.balanceOf(userAddress);
console.log(`User's balance of eDOGE tokens:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(userBalance, 5));
```

3. Approve tokens for spending

```javascript
const spenderAddress = 'SPENDER_ADDRESS';
const tokensToApprove = ethers.utils.parseUnits('1000', 5);

const approveTx = await eDOGEContract.approve(spenderAddress, tokensToApprove);
await approveTx.wait();
console.log(`Successfully approved ${ethers.utils.formatUnits(tokensToApprove, 5)} eDOGE for spending by ${spenderAddress}`);
```

4. Transfer tokens

```javascript
const recipientAddress = 'RECIPIENT_ADDRESS';
const tokensToTransfer = ethers.utils.parseUnits('500', 5);

const transferTx = await eDOGEContract.transfer(recipientAddress, tokensToTransfer);
await transferTx.wait();
console.log(`Successfully transferred ${ethers.utils.formatUnits(tokensToTransfer, 5)} eDOGE to ${recipientAddress}`);
```

5. Check allowance

```javascript
const ownerAddress = 'OWNER_ADDRESS';
const spenderAddress = 'SPENDER_ADDRESS';

const allowance = await eDOGEContract.allowance(ownerAddress, spenderAddress);
console.log(`Allowance for spender:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(allowance, 5));
```

6. Transfer tokens from another address (requires the spender to have enough allowance)

```javascript
const senderAddress = 'SENDER_ADDRESS';
const recipientAddress = 'RECIPIENT_ADDRESS';
const tokensToTransfer = ethers.utils.parseUnits('200', 5);

const transferFromTx = await eDOGEContract.transferFrom(senderAddress, recipientAddress, tokensToTransfer);
await transferFromTx.wait();
console.log(`Successfully transferred ${ethers.utils.formatUnits(tokensToTransfer, 5)} eDOGE from ${senderAddress} to ${recipientAddress}`);
```

